{"tid":1661312,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"泛民：周日九龍遊行料達數十萬人參與","createTime":"2019-10-18T04:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T06:16:53.000Z","uid":5195,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25f1be8ec76bee1df930202c326010019653f053","tid":1661312,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"【明報文章】反修例風暴至今，街頭抗爭愈見激烈，針對區議會選舉參選人、遊行申請人的暴力亦見升級。民陣正申請於周日（20日）舉辦九龍區遊行，召集人岑子杰前晚於旺角遇襲倒臥街頭，民主派內部亦瀰漫恐懼，有泛民中人相信，周日定有許多人走出來抗議暴力，有人更估計人數或達數十萬。"},{"pid":"3cef3ad6589ffa35753b8ba5ded66790e08e2123","tid":1661312,"uid":265917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:43:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>小妹發現facebook好少行動文宣流通 <br />\n我自己一個帶風向帶到好絕望</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要記住尼場革命唔係淨係屬於連登仔<br />\n<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地多數只會認同大眾都吹奏緊既野<br />\n<br />\n而藍屍page係fb大行其道<br />\n正所謂「識睇一定睇comment」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以我地要多啲係唔同post下面貼行動文宣同出下風向post </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔該大家唔好淨係focus係twitter戰線 <br />\nFB戰線一樣咁撚重要</span>"},{"pid":"c5d9aed0cb8f4d231fb6285d8a279415bf308a5c","tid":1661312,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a>"},{"pid":"c4b4610a92bf15f390a0444168616ffdbd822d36","tid":1661312,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"出左反對通知書"},{"pid":"67069ab657160b119fe3c4354c3c64fc61aa40ed","tid":1661312,"uid":7579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"行動post要上熱門！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"4e6460e430cd63dfc9b60228f44d8e8b5b3fb3f6","tid":1661312,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8553227220f19f44864e410110b3daf94aec135d","tid":1661312,"uid":7579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"１０.２０逼爆九龍"},{"pid":"d076ad6e2f56637da92377753e3a7f561b102768","tid":1661312,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba52dd7d0400a6a7f85ee0d4e8e0aa796f509d24","tid":1661312,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"10月18 7pm 面具人鏈<br />\n10月19 7pm 愛丁堡 人道救援祈禱會<br />\n10月20 1:30pm 梳士巴利花園 民陣遊行<br />\n10月25 7am 遊行式行路番工"},{"pid":"0a89a871f00e9ed5ec6ea0949122ecc30eefa561","tid":1661312,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"到時見"},{"pid":"db060d8526459083595b2ab90e25bbc79f16abab","tid":1661312,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"5b80f2897df563081dc547102f1a4af12c5e538e","tid":1661312,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ec9fdb1cd89122f1f57d3e1d62c66f41b37ca910","tid":1661312,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb6b996bc78cae5d829aefc6ae67008236984b7","tid":1661312,"uid":5195,"like":